<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/privacy.css"/>
  <title>Privacy Policy - SoulSwipe</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-800 p-8">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-4">Effective Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      At SoulSwipe, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our service.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>Account information: name, email, password (hashed), profile info</li>
      <li>Messages and interactions with other users</li>
      <li>Usage data, such as logins and swipes</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>To provide matching and messaging functionality</li>
      <li>To improve our service and user experience</li>
      <li>To enforce our terms and community guidelines</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3. Sharing Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We do not sell or rent your data. We may share it with trusted service providers for essential services (e.g., cloud hosting), or if required by law.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We use encryption, secure databases, and access controls to protect your information. However, no online service is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">You can request to delete or update your data by contacting our support team at <strong>soulhelp@soulswipe.com</strong>.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We’ll notify you of major changes on your dashboard or by email.</p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SoulSwipe. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>